{"tid":1436011,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[緊急]強烈建議連仔不如將不推文回覆變做強制","createTime":"2019-08-09T07:53:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T08:21:25.000Z","uid":160998,"like":17,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"a9d7841bd43a36ceb805411aeb6f543398cb14f3","tid":1436011,"uid":160998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T07:53:36.000Z","msg":"就算做左次標題黨教大家要用不推文回覆<br />\n但係大家好似都係唔會用 引致三毛分化撚以及無可能實行既行動post出現係熱門<br />\n<br />\n因此，強烈建議連仔將不推文回覆變做強制措施，如果想推post先禁返手掌變推文回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔知咁樣會唔會令到大家屌柒啲三毛但係啲post無咁容易上到熱門呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n正評:三毛分化撚死全家，全面落實不推文回覆！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n負評:收皮啦做完標題撚仲夠膽出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcd78fdfd090df2c07dbbf98df3e0874f0f58c32","tid":1436011,"uid":160998,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T07:54:56.000Z","msg":"手動推post！！！！"},{"pid":"9333383f67a1d7c01ceaa9243a52e83e616b6321","tid":1436011,"uid":160998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T07:55:37.000Z","msg":"推！！！！"},{"pid":"96552d8af5ee58825a33d4d47dddbaf8cd10f382","tid":1436011,"uid":160998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T07:55:51.000Z","msg":"推啊！！！！！！！！"},{"pid":"1c243af6f59919d3ce926624a25e29c5461e2837","tid":1436011,"uid":160998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T07:59:50.000Z","msg":"推！！"},{"pid":"142161bd7ef4e2f17531190fb39f8d15a38392ab","tid":1436011,"uid":10402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:00:28.000Z","msg":"agger"},{"pid":"a45dae89ab928e07c5074930684eb92f6202171b","tid":1436011,"uid":93383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:00:50.000Z","msg":"arrge"},{"pid":"406483ca4d53c15ef9899d3f23a6628eccbd1997","tid":1436011,"uid":264811,"like":0,"dislik